text: Tours Football Club, commonly known as Tours, was a football club from Tours, France. The club was founded in 1919 as AS Dock du Centre, but changed their name to Tours FC in 1951. The club was dissolved in February 2025, due to financial issues. ==Name== *1919-1951 AS Dock du Centre *1951-1993 F.C. Tours *1993-2025 Tours F.C.
